Home page: guidance, not just metrics
Phase 1 makes Home feel like a welcome page and a navigator. It includes the portal identity (logo/name), a greeting using the authenticated username, and lightweight personal stats (last login, activity highlights, owned deployments, recently used tools). More importantly, it offers curated next steps such as “Connect IDA,” “Browse Marketplace,” or “Investigate a pipeline issue,” and those cards link directly to the relevant Confluence documentation pages so the portal and docs reinforce each other.

